<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-47-0662 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper addresses the problem of greenhouse effect on global climate,and subsequent social and economic impacts. The authors advocate thatthe US should adopt a national policy that recognises the positive linksbetween energy demand, economic growth and environment protection. Recommendationsfor national strategy are given.</TEXT></DOC>